      <div class="project-sub">healthcare modelling</div>
      <p class="project-desc">
        Modelled the progression of Parkinson’s disease using patient-level features.
        Compared regression approaches and evaluated predictions through clinically relevant
        error metrics. The work highlights the challenges and opportunities in modelling
        longitudinal health data.
      </p>

      <div class="project-buttons">
        <a class="btn" href="#your-link-here">Summary</a>
        <a class="btn" href="#your-link-here">Code</a>
      </div>
