    <div class="project">
      <h3 class="project-title">Time Series Modelling & Forecasting</h3>
      <div class="project-sub">patterns over time</div>
      <p class="project-desc">
        Analysed time series to uncover structure, trends, and seasonality,
        then built and validated forecasting models using classical ARIMA/SARIMA frameworks.
        Diagnostics and error measures were used to ensure robustness.
      </p>

      <div class="project-buttons">
        <a class="btn" href="#your-link-here">Summary</a>
        <a class="btn" href="#your-link-here">Code</a>
